choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Here is an example of a healthy meal plan that meets your dietary restrictions:
Breakfast: Oatmeal with fresh fruit and nuts (such as walnuts)
Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cucumbers, tomatoes, and avocado
Dinner: Baked salmon with roasted vegetables (such as broccoli or cauliflower)
Snacks: Apple slices with almond butter, carrots with hummus.  Enjoy!
